title: 'nomination-pools: benchmark against staking-async, enable on Asset Hub Westend'
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: "Make `pallet-nomination-pools-benchmarking` depend on `pallet-staking-async`\
    \ instead of the deprecated `pallet-staking`, so nomination pools can be benchmarked\
    \ on Asset Hub.\r\n"
crates:
- name: asset-hub-westend-runtime
  bump: major
- name: westend-runtime
  bump: major
- name: pallet-nomination-pools-benchmarking
  bump: major
